Share this on WhatsAppSpread the lovePeter Nwachukwu, the husband of late gospel singer, Osinachi Nwachukwu, has said that he never hit her and that she died of lung cancer.
He was speaking at a High Court in Abuja, where he had been arraigned on Friday.
Speaking as he was being moved along, he said, “Let me tell the whole world, I have suffered a lot. I have been abandoned. What killed my wife was cancer of the lungs, I didn’t hit my wife.
“Cancer of the lungs killed my wife, Osinachi Nwachukwu, so I’m suffering for what I do not know. “
